the list of tools to build freefem++ on MacOS are:

Apple's Developer Tools



X11 

To compile ARPACK for eigen value computation 
 we need   fortran  compiler
  see  http://hpc.sourceforge.net/    and get g77 or gfortran 
  or install g77 from fink installer  
  or you can use f2c and fort77 wrapper

latex en pdflatex 

 http://tug.ctan.org/cgi-bin/getFile.py?fn=/systems/mac/mactex/MacTeX-20060314.dmg

MPI:
from http://www.lam-mpi.org/7.1/download.php

If you use the mpi version install lam-7.1.2.dmg and use xcode-2.2.1 
We try  lam-7.1.2.dmg and xcode-2.2.3 and we get linking problem with mpic++
I also try openmpi 1.0.2 and 1.1b3  but the send message  is synchronous and so some mpi examples
have dead lock.  

mpi:
http://www.lam-mpi.org/7.1/download.php


